Consistency has been my strength in my career and to do a performance so far disconnected of how I felt in training and what I thought I could do really hurts üíî
I could barely put one leg in front of the other on the run yesterday and I have no explanation for it..
I am honestly in shock that this happened on what I hoped was going to be the highlight of my career.. ü•π
Thank you to everyone for the support both on and off the course! It means a lot to me! ‚ù§Ô∏è
